  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/48221aae236f9b173a461e645065a565.avif?t=1758874889\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>The Pang series is a beloved collection of arcade video games from the early 90s. Guide two brothers on a quest around the world to save humankind from a massive alien invasion! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/065af7193b1aa48a3838c2be9706d561.webp?t=1758874889\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>For the first time in the series, the Pang Brothers come face-to-face with the nefarious Alien Commanders! These villains didn't come to Earth for the sightseeing…so get ready to blow them to smithereens!<br><br>Use your wits and skills to overcome the attack balls pouring from the skies and rescue the world’s cities and landmarks from impending annihilation<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/c1c959298b929cfd9be9e77bab391e9c.poster.avif?t=1758874889\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/c1c959298b929cfd9be9e77bab391e9c.webm?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/c1c959298b929cfd9be9e77bab391e9c.mp4?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/5b9dcd918ee5e3beecb4f541ad60a9a6.webp?t=1758874889\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br> Adventures are best shared. The couch-coop feature is available in every game mode, allowing friends and family to team up and save the world. <br>You can also show off your skills and challenge your worldwide friends to see who got the sharpest skills and can down the most balls. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/d8a3ba596203da9acc394d0a1bd70e66.webp?t=1758874889\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>● Local and Online Co-op Mode<br>● More than 100 levels <br>● Great arsenal of weapons you can use!<br>● Boss fights!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/2e8ca5be2707275d280043fb8f54e068.poster.avif?t=1758874889\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/2e8ca5be2707275d280043fb8f54e068.webm?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/2e8ca5be2707275d280043fb8f54e068.mp4?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/48221aae236f9b173a461e645065a565.avif?t=1758874889\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>The Pang series is a beloved collection of arcade video games from the early 90s. Guide two brothers on a quest around the world to save humankind from a massive alien invasion! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/065af7193b1aa48a3838c2be9706d561.webp?t=1758874889\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>For the first time in the series, the Pang Brothers come face-to-face with the nefarious Alien Commanders! These villains didn't come to Earth for the sightseeing…so get ready to blow them to smithereens!<br><br>Use your wits and skills to overcome the attack balls pouring from the skies and rescue the world’s cities and landmarks from impending annihilation<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/c1c959298b929cfd9be9e77bab391e9c.poster.avif?t=1758874889\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/c1c959298b929cfd9be9e77bab391e9c.webm?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/c1c959298b929cfd9be9e77bab391e9c.mp4?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/5b9dcd918ee5e3beecb4f541ad60a9a6.webp?t=1758874889\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br> Adventures are best shared. The couch-coop feature is available in every game mode, allowing friends and family to team up and save the world. <br>You can also show off your skills and challenge your worldwide friends to see who got the sharpest skills and can down the most balls. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/d8a3ba596203da9acc394d0a1bd70e66.webp?t=1758874889\" width=612 height=40 /></span><br><br>● Local and Online Co-op Mode<br>● More than 100 levels <br>● Great arsenal of weapons you can use!<br>● Boss fights!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/2e8ca5be2707275d280043fb8f54e068.poster.avif?t=1758874889\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/2e8ca5be2707275d280043fb8f54e068.webm?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/415150/extras/2e8ca5be2707275d280043fb8f54e068.mp4?t=1758874889\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
